title: 417 - Studio AVAILABLE NOW | Call Now For More Info
posting_body: ['At Art House, we take enormous pride in providing our residents with unequaled service in an aesthetically rich, boutique-style community.', 'Ensuring a feeling of sincere, enduring connection between ourselves and those who know Art House as home is our primary aim, and one we honor without exception.', 'Life neither begins nor ends at our doorstep, but allowing yours to thrive on both sides of it is not too much to hope for.', 'Our commitment is exactly that—allowing you to enjoy your time at home in our community, while creating a platform from which to enjoy all the Belltown neighborhood has to offer.', 'Make your home with us and come to appreciate the pleasures and peace of mind a resident-focused community can yield.', 'We are just a short walk away from Pike Place Market among many other amazing other staple Seattle places!', 'Also we are pet friendly here so bring your dogs and cats with you!', 'No breed restrictions!', 'Property Information:', 'Application: $50', 'Deposit: $300', 'Parking: $250', 'Pets(s): $35/Month', 'Utilities: $80-$125Supreme City Living at Arthouse!', 'Each home features:', '• Forced air heat', '•', 'In home laundry', '• Energy efficient appliances', '• Plank floors', '• Tile backsplashes', '• Balconies in select homes', 'Enjoy great community amenities like:', '• Two rooftop decks with grill', '• Rooftop lounge', '• Dog wash station + dog run', '• Fitness center', '• Tide dry-cleaning lockers', '• Plus Be Close to THE WATERFRONT!!!', 'Have Questions?', 'Ready to Tour?', 'Reach out!', 'Our office is open six days a week:', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'Visit <URL> to schedule a tour or apply today!', 'Offered by:', 'Blanton Turner - Arthouse', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
